---
// News — Lab updates and announcements
---

<section class="section news-section" id="news">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label animate-on-scroll">News</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Latest Updates</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="news-grid">
      <article class="news-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <time class="news-date">Jun 2026</time>
        <h3>Two papers accepted at RSS 2026</h3>
        <p>Our work on tactile-driven in-hand manipulation and sim-to-real transfer for legged locomotion will be presented at RSS in Delft.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <time class="news-date">May 2026</time>
        <h3>New quadruped fleet deployed</h3>
        <p>We received four Unitree Go2 Pro units for our multi-agent coordination research. Outdoor field trials begin next month.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <time class="news-date">Apr 2026</time>
        <h3>Industry partnership with RoboTech Corp</h3>
        <p>Signed a 3-year collaboration agreement to develop autonomous inspection robots for industrial facilities.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <time class="news-date">Mar 2026</time>
        <h3>Open-source release: EmbodiedBench</h3>
        <p>We released EmbodiedBench — a standardized evaluation suite for embodied AI policies across 12 simulation environments.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .news-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-header .section-label {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .section-header .section-label::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .news-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .news-card {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .news-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .news-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .news-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .news-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
